{
  "texts": [
    "Investigate ChatGPT's capability to supply human writers with unexpected ideas, inspiring interaction with a chatbot for novel concept development. 2.",
    "Examine how repetitive suggestions, an excess of artistic devices, and potential copyright violations might hinder human authors from utilizing ChatGPT in creative writing. 3.",
    "Evaluate whether a complete and comprehensive story concept can be generated within a single chat session, starting from a general idea and concluding with stylistic device suggestions and refinement.",
    "We have conducted a Google Scholar search to find the most relevant research articles, conference proceedings and book chapters related to the AI-agents usage in creative writing.",
    "We also studied reference lists of selected academic articles and used non-academic media references to substantiate the relevance of the issue."
  ]
}